eNCA senior reporter Barry Bateman shares more details. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - City power and emergency services are responding to a fire in an underground tunnel in the Johannesburg CBD. This fire has left Selby and surrounding areas without power. READ: Power outage affecting Joburg CBD, Selby City Power says the outage occurred after a fire in underground tunnels tripped two main lines. eNCA senior reporter Barry Bateman shares more details in the video above.